Course News

Discussing Our Husqvarna Robotic Mowers
We’re thrilled to share some exciting news with you regarding our ongoing efforts to enhance the maintenance and beauty of our course. Our team has been hard at work implementing innovative solutions, like improving efficiencies, enhancing quality and being mindful of the environment.
We look forward to seeing you soon at Orange Lake Golf Resort.

Orange Lake Golf
Golf Outings & Events
Golf Outings at Orange Lake
Orange Lake Golf provides an outstanding facility for your golf outing or event. From groups of 12 to full course use, we can arrange and personalize our facilities and menu to satisfy your event’s specifications and needs.
A fully equipped golf shop
Practice Facilities with short game area
Rental Equipment available
Specializing in Golf Event/Outing Planning
Professional tournament preparations — scoring service provided
Orange Lake is located in beautiful Orlando, Florida. The 54-hole Resort  courses are operated by Brown Golf Management.
Hosting an event? Let us see how we can help!
